  "time_ut": 1661924618,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d89\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 70\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rajapaksa have stolen 70 percent of people's savings",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Dr. Harshada Silva said that by August 2021, the value of a bank deposit of 100,000 rupees has become 30,000 rupees. He said this while joining the budget debate.",
        "\"What has happened to the savings of 30 to 40 years of work? We don't want to look from 2019 to 2022. If we look at it like that, the speaker will also suffer.",
        "See what happened from August 2021 to August 2022. If someone had saved 100,000 rupees, the value of that 100,000 rupees has decreased to 30,000 rupees this year. minus",
        "It is not wrong to say that Rajapaksa stole 70 percent of the total savings of the people, Mr. Speaker. That's the real story, that's what happened. \""
      ],
